# i18n Language File Sync Rule

When modifying i18n JSON files, **always update both language files together**:

- `new/src/i18n/en/` (English)
- `new/src/i18n/kr/` (Korean)

## Required Actions

1. When adding new keys, add to both `en` and `kr` files
2. When modifying structure (like MyServices, ToolIUse), update both files
3. When removing keys, remove from both files

## Example

If updating `kr/main_Section.json`, also update `en/main_Section.json` with the English equivalent.

```
❌ BAD: Only updating one language file
✅ GOOD: Updating both en/ and kr/ files simultaneously
```
